The SQLite section carries the new ideas: append-only build log, Peewee schema, flat MRO edges, and the distribution artifact angle. The "not committed to the repo" decision gets an explicit rationale tied back to the original XML problem — if you commit derived artifacts, they diverge from source. That felt worth naming directly.Spec store resolutionDocument · MD DownloadYou said: The implementationfile and implementationline fields recordThe implementation_file and implementation_line fields record
where an # IMPLEMENTS: <ref> marker was found in the codebase — or
