Shall I update the document?You said: is Snapshot the same as list[Component] ?is Snapshot the same as list[Component] ?8:26 AMClaude responded: Yes, essentially.Yes, essentially. A Snapshot is just a named, timestamped wrapper around a list[Component]. The id and created_at are metadata about the list, not additional content.
